id: pm-7zs0
title: Verify daily auto-release published to npm (release-health check)
description: "Recurring release-health verification. The date-based daily auto-release has silently failed before (padded-month changelog match skip; publish/Sentry-gate step failing post-tag). After any merge to main, confirm the next daily release both tagged a new vYYYY.M.D AND advanced npm 'latest'."
type: Reminder
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: "area:release",living-map,reliability
